    <refsection id="Description_LOGICAL_OP">
        <title>Description</title>
        <para>
            The Logical Operator block performs the specified logical operation on
            its inputs. An input value is TRUE (1) if it is nonzero and FALSE (0)
            if it is zero.

        </para>
    </refsection>
